{"tid":2334383,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"比特狂潮｜Musk對Tesla資產負債表轉換成Bitcoin感興趣！Saylor分享投資秘笈","createTime":"2020-12-21T06:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T09:16:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"656455aef9b7f0261996ba2537178d9fffbcf922","tid":2334383,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"虛擬貨幣Bitcoin近日破頂並升穿兩萬三美元大關，Bitcoin在美國富豪之間熱論，更吸引企業家將公司資產轉換成Bitcoin，最新被Bitcoin所吸引的是Tesla行政總裁Elon Musk，令到Musk心動的除了近期Bitcoin升勢之外，尚包括MicroStrategy行政總裁Michael Saylor。根據aax的報價，Bitcoin最新報23805美元，升1.3%。<br />\n<br />\n兩人在Twitter互動，這個話題首先由Saylor帶出，他鼓勵Musk加入Bitcoin的行列，將Tesla部份資產轉換成Bitcoin，並說：「為你的股東帶來千億美元的幫助。」並指「其他標普500指數成份股將會跟隨你的步伐，這將會為股東帶來萬億美元的幫助。」Musk顯然對此感到興趣，並問到：「是否有可能進行這麼大額的交易？」Saylor最後向Musk線下分享他的投資「秘笈」。<br />\n<br />\nMusk在2019年2月時資產淨值約1530億美元，而個人持有僅0.25個Bitcoin；至於Saylor同時財產只有5億美元，不過，他在今年投資4.25億美元在Bitcoin上，為他帶來逾2倍的財富增長。<br />\n<br />\n根據《彭博》的數據，Tesla股價今年上升8倍，令Musk財富增長1400億美元，成為全球第二大富豪，資產淨值達到1670億美元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201221/D3BXJFFFORA73NKRK2ZDIHOZQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201221%2FD3BXJFFFORA73NKRK2ZDIHOZQY%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=93515dd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201221%2FD3BXJFFFORA73NKRK2ZDIHOZQY%2F&h=930dcbce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201221/D3BXJFFFORA73NKRK2ZDIHOZQY/</a>"},{"pid":"e98b86cc0cb96223ce1813a5527e78f06702d9ea","tid":2334383,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e4f2671edc325dd087c8cdaa17ff59b59c1f34","tid":2334383,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Saylor最後向Musk線下分享他的投資「秘笈」</blockquote><br />\n教個咁多錢既人投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2e76902556370b8b3de638003b6cae274564e2","tid":2334383,"uid":120499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"Jack Dorsey 真係多撚謝你班傻鳩嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢一套現，就割Musk 同Saylor 韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4f94a02c2124996b58d45f187b147da353c4b3","tid":2334383,"uid":131551,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"財演 名人  都係度吹Bitcoin 感覺到好快大插 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f49671b94615ef2b8a1fa77e887ae3ab4ae8aca","tid":2334383,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31e4f2671edc325dd087c8cdaa17ff59b59c1f34","tid":2334383,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Saylor最後向Musk線下分享他的投資「秘笈」</blockquote><br />\n教個咁多錢既人投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}